# [{:chinese=>"为了表彰话剧界有突出贡献的艺术家和优秀话剧工作者，邮局发行了中国话剧诞辰100周年纪念邮票。", :pinyin=>"wéi le biăo zhāng huà jù jiè yŏu tú chū gòng xiàn de yì zhú jiā hé yōu xiù huà jù gōng zuò zhĕ ，yóu jú fā xíng le zhōng guó huà jù dàn chén 100zhōu nián jì niàn yóu piào 。", :english=>"In order to commend those artists and excellent workers who have made distinguished contributions to modern drama, the post office issued a set of commemorative stamps for the 100th anniversary of the birth of modern Chinese drama.", :uwc=>"16_words", :uws=>"[为了, 优秀, 作者, 发行, 周年, 工作, 年纪, 突出, 纪念, 艺术, 表彰, 话剧, 诞辰, 贡献, 邮局, 邮票]"}, {:chinese=>"不久之后，配有高分辨率显示屏的轻巧手机便可以与卫星连接，人们可以随时随地通话、收发电子邮件或者参加视像电话会议。", :pinyin=>"bù jiŭ zhī hòu ，pèi yŏu gāo fēn biàn lǜ xiăn shì píng de qīng qiăo shŏu jī biàn kĕ yĭ yŭ wèi xīng lián jiē ，rén men kĕ yĭ suí shí suí dì tōng huà 、shōu fā diàn zi yóu jiàn huò zhĕ cān jiā shì xiàng diàn huà huì yì 。", :english=>"Soon lightweight phones outfitted with high-resolution screens will be connected to satellites enabling people to talk, send and receive e-mail, or take part in video conferences anytime, anywhere.", :uwc=>"16_words", :uws=>"[不久, 之后, 人们, 会议, 分辨, 卫星, 参加, 发电, 可以, 或者, 显示, 电子, 电话, 连接, 随时, 随时随地]"}]
